Package: llmR
Title: Interface to Large Language Models with an OpenAI Compatible API
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Angelo", "D'Ambrosio", , "a.dambrosioMD@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2045-5155"))
Description: Provides an interface to various Large Language Models (LLM)
    providers (OpenAI, Azure, or other local/online endpoint). It handles prompt
    processing, rate limiting, retries, and error processing for responses.
